{
  "stem": "14867.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the reason I don't-- I'm-- as I'm talking about it, I'm thinking about my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister-in-law doesn't know how her little boy was killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And anytime I make a tape, I always wonder, how will-- how will I manage to show her, or she finds it?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if she ever reads what I say, she'll probably go crazy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I always am very hesitant about telling this story in a fear that she might sometimes, because we are very, very close friends, like sisters.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I always said to David, we will have to erase this part, if I ever say that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I imagine it's possible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then the lawyer came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We notified him right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were talking all the time that eventually we'll have to do it, but we determined not to do it as long as Mother is with us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother could have never survived this in [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Aryan. ?] Because she, first of all, her Polish was not like ours.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was with an accent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and she didn't have this kind of relationship that we had with Christian children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for us, it was-- as a matter of fact, as I told you, to me it was a help.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll tell you in a minute how that I always was-- But you knew that your mother--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that eventually-- if Mother goes, we said, we will have to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, again, this is frightening that we never said, if Mother goes, let's commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We said, if Mother goes, let's see what we can do to help ourselves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody was so determined to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is frightening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know a friend of mine, she saw her father killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
